Consider the following method:

```java
public static int[] rowSums(int[][] mat)
{
    int[] sums = new int[mat.length];
    for (int r = 0; r < mat.length; r++)
    {
        for (int c = 0; c < mat[0].length; c++)
        {
            sums[r] += mat[r][c];
        }
    }
    return sums;
}
```

